    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant attention to be roadworthy. The engine currently has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is substantial rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the rear quarter panel. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it is priced accordingly for someone willing to invest the necessary time and repairs.",
      "price": 4500.0,
